      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DUSTY RICO (1) is boxed nicely on the inside. Latest effort finished 4th on April 2 over 340m at Hobart behind Avant Danger beaten 6 lengths (19.83) in a Restricted WIN. Suited here and can find winning form. MAKE WAVES (8) has missed the frame the last couple but was a Restricted WIN winner three back (19.62) at Hobart over 340m. Can turn it around this time. STORM SIGNAL (2) showed good early burn and was there until turning but run over late to finish 7th at this track in a Grade 5. Has a good record here at this journey. The form out of last race has been strong. Worth following up. SLICK STEEL (5) will have admirers after placing last time out.",
